## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **adalimumab Humira 2015** = first FDA HS biologic. PIONEER I + II Phase 3 anti-TNF-α HSCR (HS Clinical Response) primary endpoint. immunosuppressive era 종료 + targeted biologic era 시작. quantum-VQE 의 TNF-α pocket leverage (ustekinumab + infliximab + golimumab cross-class).
2. **secukinumab Cosentyx 2023** = first FDA IL-17A HS. SUNSHINE + SUNRISE Phase 3. IL-17A axis 가 HS pathogenesis 에서 결정적 — psoriasis 와 distinct (HS = neutrophil-rich sinus). quantum-VQE 의 IL-17A pocket leverage.
3. **bimekizumab Bimzelx 2024** = first FDA IL-17A + IL-17F dual HS. BE HEARD I + II Phase 3. IL-17F homodimer + heterodimer (IL-17AF) 가 IL-17A 단독보다 broader cytokine coverage. biparatopic mAb scaffold = WEAVE 직접 fit. quantum-VQE 의 IL-17A + IL-17F dual pocket VQE 가 differentiator.
4. **povorcitinib Incyte JAK1 oral HS Phase 2/3** = first oral targeted HS (만약 승인). 비-주사제 + compliance 향상 + cost 차이. JAK1 selectivity vs. baricitinib/upadacitinib pan-JAK = safety profile 차이.
5. **spesolimab Spevigo 2022 GPP** = first FDA IL-36R. generalized pustular psoriasis 1차 적응 + research HS off-label. IL-36 axis 가 HS 의 pustular 성분과 mechanism overlap (neutrophil + IL-36 + IL-17 axis crosstalk).
6. **IL-1β anakinra + canakinumab + rilonacept** = refractory HS + Crohn HS overlap. NLRP3-inflammasome 활성화가 HS 의 sinus tract 만성염증 driver. PASI/HiSCR endpoint signal 한정 + RCT data 부족.
7. **만성 doxycycline + minocycline + clindamycin + rifampin combo** = 만성 표준 1L. anti-inflammatory + antimicrobial dual. 항생제 내성 + 장기간 (10주+) compliance 문제. dysbiosis cross-microbiome.
8. **만성 metformin + 비만 weight loss → 만성 HS 호전** = metabolic axis intervention. 비만 BMI > 30 + 만성 흡연 = HS independent risk factor. cross-obesity + metabolic + substance_use disease-modifying lifestyle intervention 가 biologic 보다 cost-effective 한 첫 step.
9. **isotretinoin Accutane vs HS** = Acne 와 distinct mechanism. Acne (피지선 + P. acnes) vs HS (apocrine + 모낭폐쇄 + neutrophil) = 별개 disease. isotretinoin HS 효과 한정. acitretin (psoriasis spillover) 도 한정.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, HS 임상 의미 한정. 만성 HS = 진단 지연 7-10년 평균 + 청소년 stigma + 정신건강 + 자살관념 cross-psychiatric 이 quantum-VQE 와 직접 연결 안 됨 — disease-axis-orthogonal limit.

